txt.en: Valdi can be found in Amdân.\n\nYou should talk to Valdi.
'You have returned with the missive? Let us see what we have here.'
DNT - 'You have done a great service for the Haban’akkâ today.'

'You have done well, but new information gathered by our scouts informs us that the top two champions were not among the defeated. Unfortunately, we don't know who they are, but the scout heard goblins saying that a missive with the Wargs' names will be arriving at Dursh Hûl soon. Go grab that missive from the goblin messenger, will you? Then we shall deal with these so-called champions.'
The enemy has been carefully watching the competition between the Wargs of Azanulbizar. The competition has narrowed down to two champions.
The goblin courier can be found on Gabilthurkhu, the Great-way, between Dursh Hûl and Kamaz-kala.\n\nValdi has asked you to retrieve a missive from the goblin courier.
